page.title: 19FAMILY LIFE
page.content: The Keenans live at Metasquoia,a 4 bedroomed house Geoff built himself on a plot of orchard land in 1974,when {Ryan}was born. Until 1978 Geoff worked as a steelworks engineer,Sandra & Ryan following him to Japan and America. They settled in Alnwick in 1978 when {Ben}was born and Geoff set up his now {flourishing kitchen & bathroom {business.}In 1984{Sadie}was born.Ryan finds it strange having a girl in the house.He enjoys{stamp & badge {collecting,playing squash & tennis, {swimming & watching T.V.}Ben likes {cricket,football,swimming,playing in {the garden & riding his bike.}Geoff spends his spare time{playing football {with Alnwick Round Table}and when Sandra isn't looking after Sadie & the boys,or doing the business accounts, she enjoys{gardening,knitting,sewing {& collecting 1st Day Stamp Covers.
